47:03.916 --> 47:04.958
Jonathan, please don't--

47:05.041 --> 47:06.250
-Just-- It'll take a minute.
-Don't do this.

47:06.333 --> 47:07.625
It's gonna just take a minute,
you're gonna rip it.

47:07.708 --> 47:09.083
-Give me one second.
-Let-- Okay, stop it.

47:09.166 --> 47:11.833
-No! I don't want you--
-JONATHAN: Stop.
