57:30.208 --> 57:31.375
PETER:<i> Sure. Is anything wrong?</i>

57:31.458 --> 57:32.958
No, I'll talk to you
in a second, just--

57:33.041 --> 57:34.500
Could you--
could you put her on?

57:34.583 --> 57:37.666
PETER:<i> Uh, sure.</i>
<i>Uh, just a second.</i>

57:37.750 --> 57:39.958
-Thanks.
-PETER:<i> Hold on.</i>

57:40.041 --> 57:42.000
-KATE:<i> Good morning.</i>
-Kate, hey, good morning.

57:42.083 --> 57:43.541
KATE:<i> Good morning.</i>

57:43.625 --> 57:49.083
Hey, so, listen, um,
look, I-- I know that, um,

57:50.375 --> 57:52.291
-that you know...
-KATE:<i> Know what?</i>

57:54.250 --> 57:57.041
...about the whole thing
with Mira.

57:57.125 --> 57:58.875
KATE:<i> Oh.</i>

57:58.958 --> 58:00.333
-Kate?
-KATE:<i> Um, I'm sorry, Jonathan.</i>

58:00.416 --> 58:02.083
No, no, Kate, Kate, hey,
hey, it's-- it's okay.

58:02.166 --> 58:04.958
I-- I understand, I know
that you couldn't, and, um...

58:05.708 --> 58:07.250
look, I just, uh-- (SIGHS)

58:08.375 --> 58:10.125
So, basically, Mira just left.

58:11.333 --> 58:14.291
-KATE:<i> How do you mean? Like...</i>
-She, um...

58:15.583 --> 58:18.083
She got in last night,

58:18.166 --> 58:20.041
and she just left
for the office,

58:20.125 --> 58:23.875
and she's going to fly out
to Tel Aviv...

58:24.625 --> 58:28.083
tonight. Yes. And, uh...

58:28.166 --> 58:30.166
KATE:<i> I'm sorry,</i>
<i>but if you two--</i>

58:30.250 --> 58:31.583
No, I-- I-- I--

58:31.666 --> 58:34.000
I know that you don't wanna
be put in the middle of this,

58:34.083 --> 58:36.583
and I just-- I just need you
to talk to her,

58:36.666 --> 58:38.875
and-- and convince her
that she needs

58:38.958 --> 58:41.416
to postpone this trip
just for a little bit,

58:41.500 --> 58:43.541
-you know? (CHUCKLES)
-KATE:<i> Postpone...</i>

58:43.625 --> 58:44.916
Yeah, just for like a couple
of weeks

58:45.000 --> 58:47.291
so that we can talk
about this calmly,

58:47.375 --> 58:49.708
and, you know,
maybe go to therapy,

58:49.791 --> 58:53.708
and it's just-- it's insanity
doing it like this overnight.

58:53.791 --> 58:57.500
KATE:<i> Well,</i>
<i>she's not doing this...</i>

58:57.583 --> 59:00.958
Did-- did you try to talk
to her?

59:01.041 --> 59:05.041
KATE:<i> Yes, I tried. But she</i>
<i>wasn't really listening...</i>

59:05.125 --> 59:06.750
