a fucking shit show?

59:09.208 --> 59:10.250
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

59:10.333 --> 59:12.958
Kate, Kate, I need--
I need you to--

59:14.208 --> 59:15.750
(CLATTERING)

59:18.583 --> 59:20.500
-PETER:<i> Hey, Jon.</i>
-Hey, Peter.

59:20.583 --> 59:22.000
PETER:<i> Why don't we come over</i>
<i>and then--</i>

59:22.083 --> 59:24.000
No, I don't-- I don't need you--
I don't need you to come over...

59:24.083 --> 59:25.125
PETER:<i> I can be there--</i>

59:25.208 --> 59:26.833
...because it's not gonna help
at all.

59:28.666 --> 59:29.666
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

59:29.750 --> 59:31.250
Yeah, yeah, it is. It is.

59:31.333 --> 59:33.458
By the way, how long
have you known about this?

59:34.583 --> 59:37.375
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

59:37.458 --> 59:38.583
Fucking--

59:38.666 --> 59:41.500
