"honesty" bullshit?

59:43.083 --> 59:44.333
PETER:<i> Look,</i>
<i>Kate's the problem--</i>

59:44.416 --> 59:46.708
No, don't-- don't blame this
on Kate. Don't blame it--

59:46.791 --> 59:49.416
I-- I called you yesterday, man.

59:49.500 --> 59:50.666
PETER:<i> I didn't wanna hurt you.</i>

59:50.750 --> 59:53.333
